{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01YQapKVxsCAHG4M7Qh3JLpR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now I have all the context I need. Let me write the `ExpressivityHierarchy.lean` file. I'll also need to add the import to `ElmanProofs.lean` if it's part of the main library.\n\nLet me write a clean, comprehensive hierarchy file that:\n1. Imports the necessary dependencies\n2. Defines formal notions needed\n3. Proves the three-part hierarchy\n\nKey dependencies:\n- `Expressivity.linear_cannot_threshold` from `LinearLimitations.lean`\n- `E1HTemporalTheorems.e1h_can_threshold` from `E1HTemporalTheorems.lean`\n\n\n- `CapacitySeparation.e88_addressable_e1h_not` from `E88ExceedsE1HCapacity.lean`\n- `E1H.e88_state_exceeds_e1h_state` from `E1HDefinition.lean`\n\nI also need to pull in the XOR results—linear networks can't compute it, but E1H can. I'm looking at the parity computation proof in E1H, though it has some gaps I'll need to work through.\n\nThe cleanest separation comes from `E1H.e1h_state_bounded`, which shows E1H outputs stay strictly within (-1, 1) across all input sequences. Linear SSMs can't guarantee this—unbounded inputs produce unbounded outputs in linear systems. That's a fundamental difference I can use to establish nonlinearity.\n\nBut I need to flip the question: what can E1H compute that linear SSMs cannot? The threshold function is the natural candidate, but E1H with tanh can only approximate it, never achieve exact equality. Looking at the formal `LinearlyComputable` predicate in the codebase, it requires exact equality between the function and the linear computation, which means I need to reconsider what the hierarchy actually captures—it's about expressivity classes defined by architectural dynamics, not perfect computation.\n\nLet me check how the other proof files like `RunningParity.lean` and `ExactCounting.lean` formalize these distinctions.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1014,"cache_read_input_tokens":72614,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1014},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"95379173-9fa9-4c3b-b84e-0caa1677a98b","uuid":"279aa31f-b8a4-45fb-9932-a6bb988032ab"}
